{
  "stem": "14900.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "What we had were the thoroughfares through the middle of the ghetto behind barbed wire on both sides and heavily guarded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And public transport went through there, German, Polish, cars, streetcars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they had two ways of getting past those across those thoroughfares.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The first one I was familiar with was SS on both sides like a border, Checkpoint Charlie thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it depended on their mood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Of course, they stood inside this warm little place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "If the weather was bad, they'd keep us there 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They could beat you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They could kick you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They could shoot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "When they decided it was time for us to cross, they'd let us cross.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The gates would open both ways, and we'd go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So when mother and I moved, we bypassed having to walk through those checkpoints in the gate.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We moved into probably an eight by ten room with a wooden floor-- excuse me, dirt floor, no wood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "For the two of us, we had one three-quarter bad, one little dresser, a table for two, and a little coal-burning stove with a couple little round holes on it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And it took up the whole room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But it was ours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And fortunately in the winter, it would warm up just from a little bit of cooking.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "This way, we were five minutes or less from work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Let me tell you about the rations in Lodz Ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know how many survivors there are from Lodz, how many of them have talked about it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were on starvation diets.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
